{"tid":897014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★又贏！【中國製造】「超級高鐵」時速1000公里，最快2年內「上路」！","createTime":"2018-11-10T14:14:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-12T11:03:39.000Z","uid":19454,"like":39,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"8c5e6acf52a3115b0012c17769bf7352cb72b02a","tid":897014,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/Highrailway525.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2FHighrailway525.jpg&h=b879711a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日，在北京舉辦的中國智慧交通大會上，由西南交通大學牽引的動力國家重點實驗室新型軌道交通技術研究所副所長鄧自剛表示，目前實驗室正在建設真空管道高溫超導磁懸浮高速試驗平台，也就是我們常說的「超級高鐵」項目，遠期實驗速度預計可以達到1000公里/小時。<br />\n<br />\n所謂的「超級高鐵」，專業術語叫做真空管道磁懸浮高速列車。磁懸浮技術使得列車懸浮在軌道上空，消除了與輪軌的摩擦，大大減小了與輪軌接觸帶來的阻力；密閉的真空管道是低氣壓環境，空氣阻力也將大大減小，同時不會受天氣的影響，比目前的高鐵更高科技。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com/techstart.presslogic.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/154088075929549700_a580x330.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3-ap-southeast-1.amazonaws.com%2Ftechstart.presslogic.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F154088075929549700_a580x330.jpg&h=93f7e163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n目前，中國高鐵的最高運營速度為350公里/小時。由於列車與輪軌之間有很大的摩擦，阻力和噪音都會隨著速度的增加而目前，國家重點實驗室正在成都搭建相關模型車試驗線，這條特製管道直徑4.2米、長140米，將在低氣壓環境中進行測試，測試時速最高可達400公里／小時，並最快將於2021年4月達到1500公里試驗時速。增加，因此需要「超級高鐵」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/10/31/article/81758/?fbclid=IwAR1HcgZk1iv0RlfKk4rx-2V4JZ1S_ENaur46EKqqgO_zkZ9iSsMoetQXQfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.presslogic.com%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2Farticle%2F81758%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1HcgZk1iv0RlfKk4rx-2V4JZ1S_ENaur46EKqqgO_zkZ9iSsMoetQXQfE&d=5r1S28h%2BdlPdArFxc0HKiv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0dc9b5e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.presslogic.com/2018/10/31/article/81758/?fbclid=IwAR1HcgZk1iv0RlfKk4rx-2V4JZ1S_ENaur46EKqqgO_zkZ9iSsMoetQXQfE</a>"},{"pid":"806afe8820b72a9722512556003bea8351e154cc","tid":897014,"uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955e5fb0f3e437cf5a480de4816a4862dc8200dc","tid":897014,"uid":188396,"like":66,"dislike":1,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:15:35.000Z","msg":"加速落地獄<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aedb84d5bacea67e876f5c4e3277bb05b749946","tid":897014,"uid":22337,"like":54,"dislike":1,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:18:07.000Z","msg":"黃泉特急<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd9aa8143b482e3c651dcecd4bda8e603feb70d","tid":897014,"uid":137921,"like":79,"dislike":1,"score":78,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20150621/large/21cf04p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20150621%2Flarge%2F21cf04p.jpg&h=d3d37a25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04c0e82e0e980849bda996d58604a31e19e35b0","tid":897014,"uid":170044,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T14:19:59.000Z","msg":"俾你研究到又點 營運又要大把錢<br />\n冇人買車飛 又繼續每年虧損<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3685d44f480787